             was indicted, for <rs id="t17841208-26-off147" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17841208-26-off147" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17841208-26-off147" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t17841208-26-cd148" type="crimeDate">18th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841208-26-off147 t17841208-26-cd148"></join> last, feloniously and falsly did make, forge, and counterfeit, or cause and procure to be falsly made, forged, and counterfeited, a certain deed, with the name 
                     <persName id="t17841208-26-person473">
                        John
                         How
                     <interp inst="t17841208-26-person473" type="surname" value="How"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841208-26-person473" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841208-26-person473" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   thereto subscribed, purporting to be a bill of sale of the said 
                     <persName id="t17841208-26-person474">
                        John
                         How
                     <interp inst="t17841208-26-person474" type="surname" value="How"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841208-26-person474" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841208-26-person474" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
